                     <interp inst="t18361128-50-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing, on the 22nd of October, 1 coat, value 7<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18361128-name-353" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18361128-name-353" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
